     AMIGADOS FOR BEGINNERS V3.1 BY FRANK BUNTON
     ===========================================

                   INSTALLATION
                   ============

Installation is simple.

1. Dearchive the file as you must already have done!!

2. Copy the drawer ANYWHERE that you like, keeping all its
   contents intact.

3. Make sure that all files are kept in their proper place.

4. Once the AmigaDOS_For_Beginners drawer is in place, all you
   need to do is:-

     Double Click on the INDEX icon

6. All the information that you need from there on can be
   read from the index.


